      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "心中只把魏虎怨，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，薛平贵。唐王晏驾，王允篡位。俺不免将金铃鸽儿放回，候公主大兵到此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "魏虎哇，贼！我不杀你誓不为人也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "苦苦害我为哪般？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵放鸽儿。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "等候公主报仇冤。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
