          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孤王上前忙遮拦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高嗣继",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "白马银枪高嗣继，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "自从盘古立地天，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵、高嗣继同起打，薛平贵跌下马。龙形上，舞，下。）"
