          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只见小将跪马前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高嗣继",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "万岁不必仔细盘，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "既愿保孤坐江山，"
        },
        {
          "character": "高嗣继",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我若保主有假意，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见小将盟誓愿，"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "西皮散板",
          "musical_style": "西皮散板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不下马，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（薛平贵想。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "薛平贵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
